sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Reconcilers
    participant NGC as Nvidia NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant TemplateAPI as Template API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ModelRegistry as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS1.2+<br/>TLS Client Cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>InferenceService
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC Resources<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Status<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,TemplateAPI: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Account<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS1.2+<br/>TLS Client Cert
        Webhook->>K8sAPI: Check API Key Secret<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>NIM Account
        Controller->>NGC: Validate NGC Account<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>API Key
        NGC-->>Controller: Account Valid + Model Catalog
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Pull Secret<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>TemplateAPI: Process Runtime Templates<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        TemplateAPI-->>Controller: Template Processed
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account Status<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Controller,ModelRegistry: Flow 3: Model Registry Integration (Optional)
        Controller->>ModelRegistry: Register Deployed Model<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token<br/>(skip verify: configurable)
        ModelRegistry-->>Controller: Model Registered
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token<br/>(TODO: migrate to HTTPS/8443)
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 5: LLMInferenceService with Gateway API
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate LLM Service<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS1.2+<br/>TLS Client Cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>LLMInferenceService
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Status<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    end
